<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 09:16:24 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国百度第三季度收入下降3%，超出市场预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-baidu-posts-3-fall-third-quarter-revenue-beats-market-estimates-2024-11-21/</link><description>百度周四公布第三季度收入下降 3%，超出市场预期，这家中国最大的互联网搜索提供商在经济低迷的情况下努力应对广告服务支出疲软的问题。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 09:09:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-baidu-posts-3-fall-third-quarter-revenue-beats-market-estimates-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>台湾特使表示，对乌克兰的军事帮助“太敏感”，但代表处是一个目标</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/military-help-ukraine-too-sensitive-rep-office-goal-taiwan-envoy-says-2024-11-21/</link><description>台湾外交部副部长吴弗朗索瓦表示，台湾没有参与对乌克兰的军事援助，因为它“太敏感”，但希望在该国设立代表处。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 08:48:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/military-help-ukraine-too-sensitive-rep-office-goal-taiwan-envoy-says-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>德国10月破产率同比增长22.9%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/insolvencies-germany-up-229-year-on-year-october-2024-11-21/</link><description>德国统计局周四表示，德国 10 月份破产企业数量比去年同期增加了 22.9%。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 08:16:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/insolvencies-germany-up-229-year-on-year-october-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国在湖南发现价值830亿美元的黄金储备</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-finds-83-billion-worth-gold-reserves-hunan-2024-11-21/</link><description>据官方媒体新华社周四报道，中国在中部湖南省发现了价值 6000 亿元人民币（合 829 亿美元）的黄金储备。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 08:09:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-finds-83-billion-worth-gold-reserves-hunan-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>中方愿就潜艇基础设施安全保持沟通</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-willing-maintain-communication-submarine-infrastructure-security-2024-11-21/</link><description>中国外交部周四表示，中方愿与有关各方保持沟通，共同维护国际潜艇基础设施安全。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 07:36:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-willing-maintain-communication-submarine-infrastructure-security-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国习近平在全球峰会上推动外交努力，为特朗普关税做好准备</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/bracing-trump-tariffs-chinas-xi-makes-diplomatic-push-global-summits-2024-11-21/</link><description>在唐纳德·特朗普连任美国领导人以来的首次全球会议上，中国国家主席习近平发起了外交攻势，对冲预期的新关税，并准备利用华盛顿与其盟友之间未来潜在的分歧。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 07:14:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/bracing-trump-tariffs-chinas-xi-makes-diplomatic-push-global-summits-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>独家：尽管美国限制，华为仍计划在 2025 年初批量生产最新的 AI 芯片</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/huawei-aims-mass-produce-newest-ai-chip-early-2025-despite-us-curbs-2024-11-21/</link><description>两位知情人士表示，中国华为计划在 2025 年第一季度开始大规模生产其最先进的人工智能芯片，尽管由于美国的限制而难以生产足够的芯片。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 06:17:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/huawei-aims-mass-produce-newest-ai-chip-early-2025-despite-us-curbs-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>中国资金枯竭，柬埔寨旗舰运河陷入困境</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/cambodias-flagship-canal-hot-water-china-funding-dries-up-2024-11-21/</link><description>在八月的一次仪式上，柬埔寨领导人洪马内跪下接受身穿藏红花长袍的僧侣的祝福，烟花和气球预示着一条运河的破土动工，他希望这条运河能够改变柬埔寨的经济命运。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 06:10:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/cambodias-flagship-canal-hot-water-china-funding-dries-up-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>HEDGEFLOW 美国对冲基金涌入中国京东、GDS：高盛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hedgeflow-us-hedge-funds-pile-into-chinas-jdcom-gds-goldman-2024-11-21/</link><description>路透社查阅的高盛报告显示，美国对冲基金第三季度加大了对在美上市中国公司的投资，其中电子商务零售商京东和数据中心运营商万国数据控股公司领投。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 06:08:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hedgeflow-us-hedge-funds-pile-into-chinas-jdcom-gds-goldman-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>ACEA 称 10 月份欧洲汽车销量持平，电动汽车取得进展</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/european-car-sales-flat-october-evs-gain-ground-acea-says-2024-11-21/</link><description>周四的行业数据显示，欧洲十月份新车销量在连续两个月下降后持平，而向纯电动或混合动力车型的过渡在本月取得了进展。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 05:07:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/european-car-sales-flat-october-evs-gain-ground-acea-says-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>集装箱托运人通过双燃料船订单对冲绿色转型</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/container-shippers-hedging-green-transition-with-dual-fuel-vessel-orders-2024-11-21/</link><description>如果绿色燃料成本太高，混合动力发动机允许运营商转向石油。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 05:05:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/container-shippers-hedging-green-transition-with-dual-fuel-vessel-orders-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>星巴克考虑与中国业务建立战略合作伙伴关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/starbucks-considers-selling-stake-chinese-business-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-11-21/</link><description>星巴克周四重申，正在为其中国业务探索战略合作伙伴关系，此前有媒体报道称该公司正在考虑将业务股份出售给当地合作伙伴。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 04:44:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/starbucks-considers-selling-stake-chinese-business-bloomberg-news-reports-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国顾问呼吁稳定2025年5%经济增长目标，加大刺激力度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-advisers-call-steady-5-2025-economic-growth-goal-stronger-stimulus-2024-11-21/</link><description>中国政府顾问建议北京维持明年5.0%左右的经济增长目标，推动采取更强有力的财政刺激措施，以减轻美国预期上调关税对中国出口的影响。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 04:14:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-advisers-call-steady-5-2025-economic-growth-goal-stronger-stimulus-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普任命卢特尼克领导美国贸易和关税后，他的对华关系受到批评</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/lutnicks-china-ties-draw-fire-after-trump-taps-him-lead-us-trade-tariffs-2024-11-21/</link><description>在当选总统唐纳德·特朗普任命投资银行家霍华德·卢特尼克领导这些已成为美中贸易战矛头的机构后，他对中国的敞口急剧增加。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 03:58:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/lutnicks-china-ties-draw-fire-after-trump-taps-him-lead-us-trade-tariffs-2024-11-21/</guid></item><item><title>由于英伟达的预测令人失望，亚洲股市表现不佳</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-11-21/</link><description>亚洲股市周四下跌，此前人工智能宠儿英伟达的收入增长放缓令投资者失望，而美元坚挺，比特币创下历史新高，受到对美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普政策希望的提振。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 03:03:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-11-21/</guid></item></channel></rss>